content: and because we have so great history already, we have decided to make it even better.
So, during june there will be so many great changes in renjuclass,
thanks to the proposals and teamwork of our senior members.
some of those changes will come you as a surprise. :)
so, approximately by the middle of June, the 4 year old Renjuclass will become more alive than ever.
but today we will celebrate our birthday.
it is a birthday to all of us.
On this wonderful day I want to thank all of you!
without you all, there would not be renjuclass,
you have made it most wonderful community
and you have proved it is possible to unite the world of renju
big big thanks to the heads of departments,
they have been most wonderful support
I am so grateful to them
they successfully built up the theory department,
and found many great teachers to teach.
We should take this chance to thank all the teachers :)
they will also manage the analyses department from june,
which is so wonderful - then I will be opening the third department here.
so, their kind work has brought renjuclass to highest level.
maybe sometimes they also feel tired from all the big work they do for class,
but the results of their work is with BIG value
we also thank our nice teachers and assistants.
many of you have tried the teaching job,
yes, they make my job easier, thanks
shuwang, span, scm2000, yyfcsd, luwenzhe....and others.
you all did a good job
but ,teacheres,we student need you .Without you ,we have no one to turn to

and its good that some famous guest teachers have agreed to teach us - zhang jinyu, klimashin, kawamura...
kawamura will teach next lesson on june 1
and finally, big big thanks to all active students,
who have been good in lessons and with homeworks and tournaments.
we still have famous teachers from out of renjuclass. :)

We will come to the celebration event!
